Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.11,0:02:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒聽說過你還有這種嗜好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八話 致人而不致於人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老張？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不僅晨練 好像連課都沒來上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非鬧肚子躺在房間裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 房間裡也看不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主公
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多要到公車過來的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德？這種時間你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼這種時間嘛 不是才剛剛放學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和朋友一起進城玩去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 你不擔心翼德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老張是老張 我是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你可是我們成都學院的君主…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐也別老是擔心別人 稍微放鬆放鬆比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個那個 你知道新開了一家店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不知道 如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃忠 黃忠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這聲音…莫非是主公？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然察覺不到老夫的氣息 真是少見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有…有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道黃忠去哪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙今早沒有去打掃院落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…從昨日起就不見翼德的蹤影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張飛也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從昨日起 玄德的舉止也有些…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些東西 持疑則模稜兩可 持信則顯而易見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是劉備玄德的臣下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不相信自己的主公 還要去相信誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信賴…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經足夠了 讀書什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 必須要多多娛樂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還年輕 多可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.79,0:06:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悶在這種深山裡 轉眼間就變老太婆了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄…玄德 這麼晚了你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐才是 這麼晚了你在別人的房前做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真閒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人這樣糾纏 我很難受的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德和黃忠都失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會發生在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啊 關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老張和黃忠不就在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德 黃忠？此前你們都去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐 你要是做出像跟蹤狂一樣的行為的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是會被你最喜歡的玄德討厭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是玄德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此路不通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.56,0:08:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主公 您這是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你礙事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.32,0:08:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬謖 快去南陽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南陽？可是 孔明大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這件事情告知給南陽君主·孫策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔明大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是逃的話 我們可就毫無樂趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼德與黃忠 不可能會以自己的意志來襲擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這樣下去糾纏不清的戰鬥會沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關羽閣下 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們成都學院裡到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子龍 難道連你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子姐也很討厭關姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,============================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙蒙今天也請假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也還是打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易找到一個適合蒙蒙的兼職
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙小姐生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.67,0:11:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午的課怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也聽不懂 PASS
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂 不要緊吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是南陽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話要向南陽君主·孫策伯符大人稟告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去成都看看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾去找蒙蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很擔心劉劉 但同樣也很擔心蒙蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公瑾哥哥 請讓我與你一同前往
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.52,0:12:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙子明嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情我聽說了 跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.87,0:12:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？沒回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 呂蒙去哪裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是從什麼時候起未歸的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…什麼時候呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仲謀？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我們走吧 公瑾哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎麼了 仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙小姐回來後 請通知我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.28,0:12:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了 仲謀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:12:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.92,0:13:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.80,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道呂蒙子明的所在了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『張流八卦超式·弓步槍手』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止吧 去山上的溫泉處洗洗汗水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張昭老師 我還可以繼續…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籠罩在心頭的暗雲沒那麼容易散卻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個放不下心中疑念之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她去了哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布布也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 公瑾 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂蒙在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.83,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是戰鬥過的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策伯符？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關羽雲長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你們會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了 關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎麼了 劉劉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然爬到那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策伯符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是南陽的大猩猩和爆乳君主嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.31,0:15:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼大家都傷痕纍纍？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說…這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下手毫不遲疑…內訌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉劉 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點都不像是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉劉 劉劉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉劉？劉劉…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 劉劉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劉劉你們無論何時…無論何地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那麼得融洽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些全都是騙人的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.09,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫策伯符 別說傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們之間的友情 容不得些許的懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不求同日生 但求同日同地死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此立誓的姐妹間的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.90,0:17:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會被斬斷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德 只不過是被人控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我和玄德二人獨處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.24,0:17:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 雜兵就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是雜兵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥過來啊 小PP砰砰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢愚弄我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.73,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種 大猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐 看來你已經做好死的思想準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是被玄德所殺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.32,0:17:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 在我眼前的人既是玄德亦非玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來要說的話裡毫無虛偽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我關羽雲長自認很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.86,0:18:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我遇到了即使付出性命也想要保護的主公
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你是個厭惡爭端的仁慈君主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會成為你的後盾而戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對自己作為鬥士而生…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.95,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到無比自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:19:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是這樣認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的相逢 是命中注定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄…德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都與你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 關姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:20:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人…有人進入了我體內
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.21,0:20:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄…德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.25,0:20:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.77,0:20:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 我的幻術竟會被破解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在找你 呂蒙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呂布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 即使到了現代也未喪失自我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.28,0:23:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誓死保護君主 關羽閣下的這份忠心值得尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 不愧是我的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.12,0:23:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『桃園之誓』可不光是嘴上說說罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我張飛一到關鍵時刻 也會奮勇上前的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.46,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張飛小姐也不要總是欺負主公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請學習一下關羽大姐的忠心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子都是揉胸捏乳的你沒資格發言
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.59,0:23:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九話 多算勝 少算不勝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs25}出自《孫子兵法》：夫未戰而廟算勝者，得算多也；未戰而廟算不勝者，得算少也。 多算勝，少算不勝，而況於無算乎。
